name: Lost In Whispers
description: Part of The Recursive Series a collection of digital arts inspired by the illustrations of the artist M.C.Escher and mystery noire TV shows from the early 20th century. A bizarre and surprising universe created using recursive algorithms in old photos and movie frames, generating a contemporary look from the past.
